data.description: 4.97 acre property in Gahanna Schools. Four stall horse barn with tack room and sawdust room. Two deep parking/workshop bays and 20x40 hay loft. Barn is approximately 40x46 with electric and water. House is a 3 bedroom (two on the first floor and the primary on the 2nd), two full baths (one on the first level and one on the 2nd). The home has many upgrades including remodeled bath and kitchen on the first floor and remodeled bath on the second floor. Home is now connected to city water and natural gas. HVAC was replaced in 2017. Refinished hardwood flooring and replaced carpet with hardwood floors. Many other updates also. Beautiful country living minutes from city amenities.
